# Task #124: engine exit 6 (PAIRING_EXPIRED) during fetch-on-launch — the hook shows the
# actionable cause, flags the shared .pairing-expired file for the Tools-menu banner, and
# leaves the stub intact (task #120 failure contract).
desc fetch hook (#124): PAIRING_EXPIRED (rc=6) — actionable message + menu flag + intact stub
invoke prehook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
sdfile Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
engine 6|PAIRING_EXPIRED
expect_exit 0
expect_trace SHOW2 simple text='Pairing expired — open Tools > Lodor to re-pair'
expect_file Tools/tg5040/Lodor.pak/.pairing-expired
expect_file_empty Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✘ Zelda.gba
